model.state

Class ByteState

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.state.ByteState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    State

    public class ByteState
extends java.lang.Object
implements State
    Implements the State interface as a byte value, where 0 represents dead and 1 represents alive. Needs memory profiling on Turing Machine pattern.
